<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[الشامة]</span>: العلامة،<span class="c5"> واحدة:</span> الشام.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
